      "content": "i hear you but i'm literally stuck at home and i dont have anything else to do. it's just a tiny little cyst, it's not like it's my heart or anything lol. i've used neosporin on cuts a million times before and it always works. if i just do a warm compress for 10 mins like 3 times a day and keep the ointment on it, what's the actual worst that could happen? can't i just try that for 24 hours and see if it gets better before i go spend all that money on a doctor?",
